class.doc:
{@link Credential} implementation that is used to authorize OAuth2 enabled requests through the use of the access_token header, as well as refresh the token when it is required. It is important that access to this class be made from within a managed JDO context and that the persistence manager be closed in a finally block to save any updates to the access token.
This class is safe to use from multiple threads.
@author moshenko@google.com (Jacob Moshenko) @since 1.4

